1. Installed NVM to manage Node versions:
   curl -o- https://raw.githubusercontent.com/nvm-sh/nvm/v0.39.7/install.sh | bash

2. Closed and reopened the terminal, then installed Node version 20.16.0:
   nvm install 20.16.0
   nvm use 20.16.0

3. Installed SASS using npm:
   npm install sass
